Class PlotDataManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • is201.g5t08.farmcity.dao.PlotDataManager

  • public class PlotDataManager
extends java.lang.Object
    The Class PlotDataManager keeps a key-value store of the user's plots. The key is the User's username and the value is a List of Plots.
